description: Care Instructions: Hand Wash Only  , Start your day with confidence knowing you have a reliable companion to carry your laptop and personal belongings. Introducing the Lavie Sport Chairman laptop backpack, a versatile and spacious option for the modern-day commuter. Equipped with a padded laptop compartment that fits up to 14" laptops, you can be sure your device is well-protected on the go  , Featuring a pass-through trolley handle on the back panel, you can easily secure your backpack to your luggage while navigating the airport or train station. The front pocket is thoughtfully designed with multiple zippered organizers for your keys, pens, cell phone, and power bank, keeping your essentials within reach  , Built with water-resistant polyester fabric and synthetic leather, this backpack can withstand unexpected showers or spills. Plus, the mesh padded shoulder straps ensure comfort and ease of use, even on long days  , Convenience is key, and this backpack delivers with a fabric pocket on one side panel for holding a water bottle or compact umbrella. With external dimensions of length 30cm, width 16cm, and height 43cm, this backpack has a capacity of 24 litres  , Trust in the durability of this backpack and rest easy knowing it comes with a manufacturer warranty of 12 months. The Lavie Sport Chairman laptop backpack - a reliable choice for the daily commuter
